ai-patthana22.18:0.2_0: under the influence of the Dhamma: the Protector of the Three Worlds
ai-patthana22.18:1.1_0: One doesn’t give rise to the cause or reason for causes.
ai-patthana22.18:1.1_1: or causes and reasons to give rise to the teaching.
ai-patthana22.18:1.1_2: or causes and reasons to teach.
ai-patthana22.18:2.1_0: One who doesn’t cause the teaching to give rise to the cause or reason for causes.
ai-patthana22.18:2.1_1: not arises in him to teach the Dhamma to someone who is not Dhamma, or to cause two things.
ai-patthana22.18:3.1_0: Neither in line with the teaching is not Dhamma for the sake of linking,
ai-patthana22.18:3.1_1: Not principles, or results in line with the teaching.
ai-patthana22.18:4.1_0: or causes and reasons not give rise to unprincipledity. ...
ai-patthana22.18:5.1_0: not the teaching for the sake of nature ...
ai-patthana22.18:6.1_0: not the cause or condition for the sake of purification or cause.
ai-patthana22.18:6.1_1: not the cause or reasons to give up or cause or reason.
ai-patthana22.18:6.1_2: eleven reasons based on the basis of conditioned objects, ninety-two objects,
ai-patthana22.18:7.1_0: or causes and reasons not give rise to the teaching for the sake of purification.
ai-patthana22.18:7.1_1: the nine have causes and reasons.
